movie.title: Quarantine L.A.
movie.description_intro: A group of seven strangers try to survive and escape from isolated Los Angeles that has been infected by a strange, human changing virus.
movie.description_full: A group of seven strangers try to survive and escape from isolated Los Angeles that has been infected by a strange, human changing virus.

movies.title: I Feel Pretty
movies.summary: In I FEEL PRETTY a woman who struggles with feelings of deep insecurity and low self-esteem, that hold her back everyday, wakes from a brutal fall in an exercise class believing she is suddenly a supermodel. With this newfound confidence she is empowered to live her life fearlessly and flawlessly, but what will happen when she realizes her appearance never changed?

movies.title: Battle Circus
movies.summary: Nurse Lt. Ruth McGara is assigned to a Mobile Army Surgical Hospital (MASH) unit near the front lines of the Korean War. There she meets and is roughly romanced by Major Jed Webbe, one of the unit's surgeons. Webbe is pushy and seems to care only for momentary pleasures, but McGara falls for him just the same. Their romance blossoms in the midst of overwhelming numbers of casualties, threats from the enemy and from the weather, and emergency evacuations that test the mettle of even a unit whose very name suggests quick mobility.

movies.title: Culloden
movies.summary: A reconstruction of the Battle of Culloden, the last battle to take place on British soil, as if modern TV cameras were present.

movies.title: Jurassic Prey
movies.summary: A woman steals money from her mob boss husband hoping to start a new life with her lover. Meanwhile, a washed-up former child star and his buddies rob a bank with a police detective hot on their trail. Through a twist of fate, these people all find themselves at a remote cabin, unaware that recent construction work has unleashed a ferocious creature which now roams the surrounding area! Who will survive in MEATEATERS!
